78
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:48,884
Hi.

79
00:04:49,004 --> 00:04:50,137
Oh, hi, Penny.

80
00:04:50,257 --> 00:04:54,239
FYI, the hot water is inadequate
on machine two, so colors only,

